This paper discusses machine learning development and deployment for edge devices, which involves topics such as deep learning, computer vision, artificial intelligence, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.EM (Emerging Technologies), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
